videos.title: How Many Cheerios Does it Take to Win on Turn 2?   Much Abrew
videos.description:
Cheerios died when Mox Opal was banned, but now it's back, so let's see if we can get some turn two kills with a deck overflowing with janky zero mana equipment!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.cardkingdom.com/mtggoldfish
